WEBVTT

01:41.320 --> 01:43.160
When the world just began,

01:43.240 --> 01:46.360
Pan Gu's spirit became the Dragon Deity.

01:47.120 --> 01:50.440
He had nine sons.
Calamity came from Jiu Ying.

01:51.080 --> 01:53.240
Jiu Ying was the lord of all demons.

01:53.840 --> 01:55.680
He plunged the world into chaos

01:55.760 --> 01:58.440
and sparked endless war
between men and demons.

01:58.520 --> 02:00.320
Bodies covered the land.

02:01.000 --> 02:03.680
To save all living beings,

02:03.760 --> 02:05.600
the nine dragon sons
fought Jiu Ying to the death.

02:06.480 --> 02:10.080
Eight of them
turned into towering mountains

02:10.160 --> 02:12.000
to seal Jiu Ying away.

02:12.600 --> 02:15.760
Only the ninth son, Chi Wen,

02:15.840 --> 02:19.800
remained in the world to guard all life.

02:36.480 --> 02:40.960
TEN YEARS AGO

03:21.040 --> 03:23.800
Who are you? Where are you from?

03:27.240 --> 03:28.560
I don't remember.

03:29.920 --> 03:30.880
What's your name?

03:33.320 --> 03:35.160
You don't remember your name either?

03:39.920 --> 03:41.320
What do you remember then?

03:44.000 --> 03:45.320
I think…

03:47.960 --> 03:49.560
I have a younger brother.

03:53.520 --> 03:55.760
Why were you outside the Shilin Sect?

03:58.120 --> 03:59.400
I don't know.

04:03.200 --> 04:07.480
I just felt… a voice is calling me.

04:09.280 --> 04:10.760
It told me to come here.

04:13.440 --> 04:14.600
That's fine.

04:16.279 --> 04:17.560
You can stay here.

04:33.080 --> 04:34.560
Fierce wind, driving rain.

04:35.800 --> 04:37.160
Reborn after calamity.

04:38.920 --> 04:40.320
I'll name you after this image…

04:43.480 --> 04:44.560
Li Jie.

04:46.120 --> 04:47.520
Li Jie…

04:51.720 --> 04:53.200
You're very strong.

04:53.920 --> 04:56.160
The Shilin Sect has no weapon fit for you.

04:57.240 --> 04:59.080
Go to Mount Nandang.

04:59.160 --> 05:01.280
A long knife left behind
by a mountain demon

05:02.600 --> 05:04.520
is stuck at its peak.

05:04.600 --> 05:06.200
No one has been able to pull it out.

05:07.040 --> 05:08.360
Give it a try.

06:04.280 --> 06:05.360
Ji Ling.

06:17.640 --> 06:20.040
The Shilin Sect is a terrible place.

06:20.880 --> 06:24.200
Chained by spells, caged by wards.

06:25.280 --> 06:27.600
They don't just strip demons
of their painted human skins,

06:29.200 --> 06:31.240
but also change the hearts of people.

06:37.840 --> 06:39.120
Feeling guilty?

06:40.200 --> 06:42.360
My lofty Master Dragon Deity?

06:43.000 --> 06:45.360
I like you more when you're Ji Ling.

06:46.200 --> 06:47.600
To me,

06:49.600 --> 06:52.880
innocent, sweet Ji Ling
is much more interesting.

06:55.560 --> 06:58.080
A fox from the Formless Moon,
do you even have a heart?

06:59.320 --> 07:01.440
You dare speak of "like"?

07:04.120 --> 07:05.320
A heart?

07:06.120 --> 07:07.640
Of course I have.

07:10.200 --> 07:14.360
If you can't feel it,
you can touch it and see.

07:20.360 --> 07:22.040
Are you shy now?

07:22.960 --> 07:25.440
We shared so much at the Wei mansion.

07:25.520 --> 07:26.760
Have you forgotten?

07:29.400 --> 07:30.920
Or maybe…

07:33.080 --> 07:34.120
you're afraid of me?

07:43.040 --> 07:44.520
You are Ji Ling.

07:45.560 --> 07:48.880
Why else would you suddenly show up

07:48.960 --> 07:51.800
and free me from all these spells?

07:54.640 --> 07:56.520
You couldn't bear to see me hurt.

07:57.120 --> 07:58.600
Couldn't bear to see me scarred.

07:59.960 --> 08:02.520
The wound on your neck looks pretty deep.

08:02.600 --> 08:05.680
If you don't treat it properly,
it will leave a scar.

08:06.480 --> 08:07.480
Am I right?

08:09.880 --> 08:11.200
Since ancient times,

08:12.000 --> 08:15.000
the Formless Moon and Shilin Sect
keep out of each other's way,

08:15.080 --> 08:17.080
each showing great restraint.

08:17.160 --> 08:20.840
If a Formless Moon fox
dies in the Shilin Sect's hall,

08:21.720 --> 08:24.240
that's a headache I don't want.

08:29.400 --> 08:32.240
I'll overlook your trespassing.

08:32.760 --> 08:34.200
I'll have someone escort you out.

08:35.159 --> 08:36.200
And take this.

08:38.360 --> 08:42.240
You risked coming here
surely for this thing, right?

09:02.200 --> 09:04.400
What if I have another purpose?

09:05.040 --> 09:07.160
What if I want to stay with you?

09:13.280 --> 09:17.160
Master, you bathe
and scent yourself every day?

09:19.800 --> 09:21.600
This fragrance on you is so unique.

09:21.680 --> 09:23.920
I've never smelled it anywhere else.

09:25.400 --> 09:26.840
But this smell…

09:28.800 --> 09:30.880
leaves my heart feeling empty,

09:31.920 --> 09:37.280
like a valley full of flowers
but empty of people.

09:41.200 --> 09:42.520
Master,

09:48.360 --> 09:50.120
are you lonely?

09:53.440 --> 09:55.240
Want me to stay with you?

10:05.080 --> 10:06.320
Such a bad act.

10:07.240 --> 10:08.680
Stop pretending.

10:09.920 --> 10:13.800
Formless Moon foxes excel at fake feelings

10:14.680 --> 10:15.720
and word manipulation.

10:16.800 --> 10:18.080
To get what they want,

10:18.160 --> 10:21.960
they wear a thousand faces
and whisper sweet nothings.

10:22.880 --> 10:25.040
Under such a pretty face,

10:26.480 --> 10:28.480
what a cold heart hides.

10:29.280 --> 10:31.040
You know it well yourself.

10:34.840 --> 10:36.000
You too.

10:36.760 --> 10:38.600
Under such a pretty face,

10:39.200 --> 10:41.320
what a cold heart hides.

10:42.400 --> 10:44.480
You know it well yourself.

10:52.680 --> 10:53.840
You are not Ji Ling!

10:55.040 --> 10:56.760
You've got your jade jue back.

10:58.080 --> 10:59.440
If you don't want to fade away,

11:00.600 --> 11:02.800
take this token and leave.

11:44.320 --> 11:45.400
You're awake?

11:47.360 --> 11:50.840
-I'm in the Shilin Sect?
-Yeah. Are you feeling better?

11:52.200 --> 11:55.560
Ji Ling… really is the Dragon Deity?

11:55.640 --> 11:57.280
To be honest,

11:57.360 --> 12:00.280
this is our first time
seeing Master's true form.

12:00.800 --> 12:02.160
Even you can't recognize the Dragon Deity?

12:02.760 --> 12:04.920
Master Chi Wen
stays in the Scale Cave all year.

12:05.000 --> 12:07.760
Only Commander Li
and his personal attendants serve him.

12:07.840 --> 12:10.520
How could ordinary hunters like us
ever get to see him?

12:10.600 --> 12:11.880
But, come to think of it,

12:11.960 --> 12:14.280
the flowerless young hunter Ji Ling,

12:14.360 --> 12:17.080
who always joked with us
and hunted demons by our side,

12:17.160 --> 12:18.760
turned out to be the Dragon Deity himself.

12:26.160 --> 12:28.360
Master, the new puppet is here.

13:38.840 --> 13:39.680
Master!

13:57.560 --> 13:59.400
Master, you're so powerful!

14:00.160 --> 14:03.960
No matter how badly I'm hurt,
you can heal me completely,

14:04.040 --> 14:06.000
without even leaving a scar.

14:06.920 --> 14:11.320
But… I let you down this time.

14:11.400 --> 14:13.920
I failed my mission
and didn't bring Xiaowei here.

14:15.520 --> 14:17.640
You did very well.

14:18.760 --> 14:19.720
Get some rest.

14:21.000 --> 14:24.320
Next, more important tasks await you.

14:26.680 --> 14:29.960
Whatever the mission, I'll give it my all!

14:37.680 --> 14:40.800
Oh, right. Xiaowei gravely wounded me.

14:41.760 --> 14:45.120
What about Miss Lu and her partner?
Were they hurt?

14:45.200 --> 14:47.080
They've returned to the Formless Moon.

14:51.200 --> 14:54.000
Lu Wuyi just left this place.

15:02.800 --> 15:06.960
Master, if there's nothing else,
I'll take my leave now.

15:07.840 --> 15:09.040
Go on.

15:09.120 --> 15:10.040
Wait.

15:18.280 --> 15:20.280
-Thank you, Master.
-Go on.

15:30.920 --> 15:32.480
What are you worried about?

15:34.360 --> 15:38.360
I'm afraid that naive boy
has fallen in love.

15:40.960 --> 15:42.040
Love?

15:43.880 --> 15:47.880
A puppet that was made,
how could he feel love?

15:49.160 --> 15:51.200
But he's always believed

15:51.280 --> 15:55.800
he's a little fox you saved
at the foot of South Mountain.

16:00.600 --> 16:02.880
Then let him keep believing.

16:04.360 --> 16:05.720
What's wrong with that?

16:06.680 --> 16:08.560
He's just a simple puppet with no heart,

16:09.400 --> 16:12.000
and she's just
a demon fox with no feelings.

16:42.120 --> 16:43.160
Wangyan.

16:44.800 --> 16:47.800
This is far enough. Safe travels, ladies.

16:48.480 --> 16:49.760
Thank you, sir.

16:51.840 --> 16:52.680
Wait.

16:54.040 --> 16:57.120
Miss Lu, you need to return that token.

17:35.560 --> 17:36.880
Lu Wuyi?

17:38.520 --> 17:40.920
Lu Wuyi? Lu Wuyi?

17:42.600 --> 17:44.720
Lu Wuyi?

17:47.360 --> 17:48.440
Lu Wuyi?

17:56.000 --> 17:57.320
Should we stop?

18:00.400 --> 18:01.680
Lu Wuyi?

18:06.240 --> 18:07.560
Lu Wuyi?

18:14.200 --> 18:15.680
Lu Wuyi?

18:23.160 --> 18:24.280
Lu Wuyi?

18:25.920 --> 18:29.640
We're just passing strangers.
We can't even tell what's real.

18:30.280 --> 18:31.680
Why stop?

18:36.880 --> 18:38.200
Lu Wuyi…

18:45.320 --> 18:46.400
Lu Wuyi…

19:44.400 --> 19:46.720
Miss Lu, there you are.

19:54.560 --> 19:58.400
Why are you wearing that robe?

20:01.200 --> 20:04.280
That annoying Dragon Deity
ruined my clothes.

20:04.360 --> 20:05.360
Then, afraid people would gossip,

20:06.600 --> 20:10.560
he had his attendant
give me this ugly robe.

20:13.120 --> 20:14.680
That robe…

20:16.320 --> 20:17.520
is mine.

20:20.480 --> 20:21.440
Is it?

20:26.480 --> 20:27.520
Here you are!

20:47.280 --> 20:50.760
Your hands are dirty from picking flowers.

20:53.720 --> 20:54.960
It's fine!

20:55.800 --> 21:00.000
You said you love flowers most.

21:01.720 --> 21:02.880
So I picked some.

21:03.960 --> 21:05.600
You remember I love flowers?

21:10.600 --> 21:15.920
The mighty Dragon Deity stooped so low
as to pick flowers himself?

21:17.840 --> 21:20.640
I… I'm not…

21:21.440 --> 21:24.120
I know you're not. You're Ji Ling.

21:30.760 --> 21:32.280
Sure, I love flowers…

21:34.680 --> 21:38.040
but out here, they're all over the hills.

21:39.440 --> 21:41.520
You ran all the way here, out of breath.

21:42.680 --> 21:43.560
It wasn't worth it.

21:44.440 --> 21:45.720
No, it was.

21:45.800 --> 21:49.880
These only bloom in the Shilin Sect.
They're different.

21:50.840 --> 21:52.160
After you go back,

21:53.080 --> 21:56.240
when you see these flowers, maybe…

21:57.280 --> 21:58.680
they'll remind you of me.

22:08.120 --> 22:09.960
Flowers are pretty…

22:12.160 --> 22:14.040
but they'll wilt soon.

22:16.480 --> 22:17.680
We can't keep them.

22:20.280 --> 22:21.560
Even if I miss you,

22:22.520 --> 22:25.640
it won't last… more than a few days!

22:27.400 --> 22:28.720
That's okay.

22:28.800 --> 22:33.200
Next time, I'll make you
a flower that never wilts.

22:33.280 --> 22:34.120
Deal?

22:36.080 --> 22:37.160
Next time?

22:38.280 --> 22:43.120
Anyway, we will meet again, won't we?

22:47.960 --> 22:48.920
Then I'll wait for it.

23:20.160 --> 23:22.080
How… will I find you then?

23:23.280 --> 23:25.880
Don't worry. I'll find you.

23:30.760 --> 23:34.960
Miss Lu, your boat is already gone.
I'll call another one for you.

23:35.680 --> 23:36.720
Miss Lu…

24:18.600 --> 24:20.320
You like him?

24:22.680 --> 24:24.600
I just like flowers.

24:32.520 --> 24:33.480
You can't keep them.

24:39.120 --> 24:40.400
I know.

25:05.200 --> 25:07.560
Oh man! How did
the Dragon Deity's Power get into you?

25:13.440 --> 25:14.560
Where are we?

25:15.880 --> 25:17.160
We're in the Shilin Sect.

25:19.920 --> 25:21.480
We're done for.

25:22.360 --> 25:25.240
-Chickens in a weasel's den!
-Yeah, you're one.

25:29.800 --> 25:32.760
I've never seen
that six-eyed butterfly demon before.

25:33.360 --> 25:35.640
He calls himself Yuan Wuhuo.

25:41.360 --> 25:42.480
Yuan Wuhuo?

25:43.120 --> 25:47.000
Yes. That name sounded kind of familiar.

25:47.080 --> 25:51.760
So, I went to Wanlin Pavilion
and looked through the sect archives.

25:52.400 --> 25:54.280
Sure enough, a hundred years ago,

25:54.360 --> 25:58.640
a hunter commander in our sect
also named Yuan Wuhuo.

25:59.240 --> 26:01.680
However, his name meant "no calamity".

26:02.280 --> 26:04.440
Just one character
different from the butterfly demon's.

26:19.760 --> 26:23.920
Commander Yuan Wuhuo passed away long ago.

26:25.120 --> 26:28.000
But there's something strange
about Yuan Wuhuo this time.

26:29.240 --> 26:34.040
He looks… exactly like Commander Li Jie.

26:37.920 --> 26:42.680
I heard Commander Li lost his memory
and has never found his past.

26:43.520 --> 26:47.400
Could the two of them
be connected somehow?

26:49.600 --> 26:52.280
One's a demon, one's a human.

26:53.000 --> 26:54.240
How could they be connected?

26:55.440 --> 26:58.280
When a demon takes human form,
the first skin they paint

26:58.360 --> 27:01.680
is often made from something
lost by a human.

27:02.520 --> 27:04.400
So they take on the owner's appearance.

27:05.280 --> 27:09.040
Maybe this butterfly demon
found something from Li Jie

27:09.680 --> 27:11.280
and took his form.

27:13.480 --> 27:14.720
Fair enough.

27:17.120 --> 27:20.640
For now, let's keep this from Li Jie.

27:23.160 --> 27:24.240
Yeah.

27:24.960 --> 27:30.160
If that stern commander of ours
found out some demon borrowed his face,

27:30.240 --> 27:32.720
he'd probably explode with rage.

27:39.760 --> 27:42.040
-Master.
-You're here.

27:42.640 --> 27:46.080
Mr. Bai Ze, what brings you here?

27:46.880 --> 27:48.880
I know all things in the world.

27:49.840 --> 27:51.880
Something's troubling my master.

27:53.200 --> 27:54.800
I'm here to help.

27:56.040 --> 27:57.920
Master, you want to ask

27:58.520 --> 28:02.360
why the Dragon Deity's Power
got into Wu Shiguang, right?

28:03.240 --> 28:04.320
Why?

28:05.760 --> 28:07.040
Because of this.

28:09.760 --> 28:12.600
That string of prayer beads?
What's their story?

28:13.600 --> 28:15.360
They're called the Twelve Thoughts.

28:16.200 --> 28:18.320
Each bead is made from a dragon fang,

28:18.400 --> 28:23.440
so they can carry sinners' blood
and the Dragon Deity's Power.

28:24.280 --> 28:27.280
I'm guessing the Dragon Deity's Power

28:27.360 --> 28:29.120
must've sensed the dragon aura

28:30.120 --> 28:31.560
and was drawn to them.

28:32.960 --> 28:34.560
So it's thanks to the dragon fangs.

28:35.800 --> 28:37.960
They were your master's legacy, right?

28:39.760 --> 28:40.840
He was really something,

28:42.360 --> 28:43.920
stealing teeth from a dragon!

28:44.960 --> 28:46.520
So many dragon fangs…

28:47.320 --> 28:49.880
Wu Shiguang is just a folk hunter.

28:49.960 --> 28:51.800
Where could he have gotten them?

28:53.000 --> 28:55.000
The first owner of the Twelve Thoughts,

28:55.600 --> 28:58.520
legend says, was a corrupted demon monk.

28:59.080 --> 29:03.560
Mo Yuntan, continue gathering
the spirit fragments of Jiu Ying.

29:03.640 --> 29:06.040
I have other matters
to discuss with Bai Ze.

29:08.000 --> 29:09.120
Yes, sir.

29:09.200 --> 29:10.840
Maybe soon,

29:11.760 --> 29:14.600
all you double-flower hunters
can lay down your burdens

29:15.520 --> 29:18.920
and stop toiling across this vast land.

29:32.600 --> 29:34.120
It's not because of those prayer beads.

29:35.600 --> 29:36.960
I know.

29:38.280 --> 29:39.520
This day…

29:41.560 --> 29:43.240
has finally come.

30:12.920 --> 30:14.600
THE DRAGON DEITY WILL FALL

30:14.680 --> 30:16.320
THE FORMLESS MOON WILL RISE

30:18.080 --> 30:19.480
"The Dragon Deity will fall."

30:20.080 --> 30:21.200
"The Formless Moon will rise."

30:32.400 --> 30:33.920
After Jiu Ying was sealed,

30:34.000 --> 30:36.720
the demons lost their leader
and scattered across the land.

30:37.320 --> 30:42.360
Many of them are lurking and scheming
to free Jiu Ying.

30:44.120 --> 30:47.360
The one behind Xiaowei's broken vow

30:48.160 --> 30:50.000
is after the Dragon Deity's Power.

30:50.800 --> 30:54.040
Only that power can kill a dragon.

30:54.120 --> 30:57.440
And the last fragments
of the Dragon Deity's Power

30:58.040 --> 31:00.680
reside in you four high-rank demons.

31:01.280 --> 31:05.560
Whoever gathers all four first
can kill the dragon.

31:06.720 --> 31:08.360
If the Dragon Deity falls,

31:09.640 --> 31:11.360
Jiu Ying's seal will shatter,

31:12.120 --> 31:13.880
and chaos will consume the world.

31:15.640 --> 31:19.320
So… is Wu Shiguang the one
we've been waiting for?

31:20.960 --> 31:22.400
You could say yes,

31:24.560 --> 31:26.040
but also no.

31:27.320 --> 31:29.360
Hide them already.

31:30.640 --> 31:31.960
We've sneaked in now.

31:32.560 --> 31:34.000
What's the next move?

31:34.760 --> 31:36.760
-Wait.
-Wait?

31:40.080 --> 31:42.960
Wait for the right moment and do our best.

31:45.640 --> 31:46.960
"Do our best"?

31:48.280 --> 31:50.160
Isn't that my family motto?

31:50.240 --> 31:51.520
You sure remember it well.

31:53.600 --> 31:54.480
How come you remember it so well?

31:58.000 --> 31:59.280
Some things…

32:05.240 --> 32:06.440
are different now.

32:06.960 --> 32:08.840
So what's your plan?

32:09.680 --> 32:12.480
I've sent Li Jie and Ji Ling
to retrieve the prayer beads.

32:14.640 --> 32:16.280
I want him to know

32:17.560 --> 32:20.880
I refuse to remain
a powerless Dragon Deity.

32:22.800 --> 32:25.120
I'll take back my supreme power.

32:26.720 --> 32:29.560
I want people to worship me
for all eternity,

32:32.600 --> 32:34.240
to revere me as a god.

32:34.880 --> 32:35.840
Wu Shiguang?

32:36.720 --> 32:37.960
See? Opportunity knocks.

32:48.440 --> 32:53.320
Master, you're here
to take back your power from me?

32:55.160 --> 32:57.280
-I…
-Hand over the prayer beads.

32:59.160 --> 33:01.320
Since you want them,

33:03.520 --> 33:04.920
I should return them sincerely.

33:05.840 --> 33:07.080
Don't worry.

33:07.160 --> 33:10.480
Once we extract the power inside,
we'll give the beads back to you.

33:13.880 --> 33:15.120
Stop right there!

33:22.160 --> 33:23.600
I've waited for this moment…

33:25.400 --> 33:26.840
for far too long.

33:29.040 --> 33:31.000
If I'd known you were the Dragon Deity,

33:32.480 --> 33:35.840
I would have killed you
back at the Wei mansion.

33:53.040 --> 33:55.280
He scared me to death!
Hey, you fight dirty!

33:58.520 --> 34:00.080
Don't… Don't kill me!

34:05.960 --> 34:07.200
Stop!

34:30.040 --> 34:31.040
Demon marks!

34:33.239 --> 34:34.239
You're a demon?

34:35.719 --> 34:40.120
Wu Shiguang is the sole survivor
of the flood dragon clan's massacre.

34:41.520 --> 34:44.920
So he's here to avenge his people?

34:49.239 --> 34:50.320
That's right.

34:51.239 --> 34:52.560
I am a demon,

34:55.600 --> 34:56.800
one of the flood dragon clan.

34:57.920 --> 35:02.480
Back then, you sent Shilin Sect hunters
to slaughter all my kin.

35:09.880 --> 35:14.400
You claimed to end the war
between men and demons,

35:15.080 --> 35:18.800
but in secret, you feared
Jiu Ying would break free

35:18.880 --> 35:20.360
and let the demons rise.

35:21.360 --> 35:23.760
So you ordered hunters

35:23.840 --> 35:27.520
to wipe out every demon clan in advance!

35:29.240 --> 35:31.480
The Dragon Deity wiped out your clan?

35:34.400 --> 35:35.400
What's wrong?

35:37.120 --> 35:40.920
You killed too many demons
to remember this massacre?

35:47.560 --> 35:48.640
Since you're a demon,

35:49.480 --> 35:51.720
I can't let you keep
the Dragon Deity's Power.

35:53.920 --> 35:55.840
Hand over the beads, and I'll let him go.

36:05.040 --> 36:06.800
"The Dragon Deity will fall."

36:08.160 --> 36:12.920
Master, you once said
only a dragon can kill a dragon.

36:13.560 --> 36:15.840
The eight dragon sons
sacrificed themselves,

36:15.920 --> 36:16.840
standing as mountains.

36:17.880 --> 36:19.600
Only Chi Wen remains.

36:20.360 --> 36:22.800
Who is left to kill him?

36:24.000 --> 36:28.000
Whoever holds the Dragon Deity's Power.

36:29.040 --> 36:33.840
Now, Chi Wen's under siege
from his own former power.

36:56.240 --> 36:58.920
According to the Oracle Stone's
latest prophecy,

37:00.320 --> 37:04.280
Wangyan and I are going
to protect the Dragon Deity?

37:05.800 --> 37:06.760
No.

37:08.280 --> 37:09.760
You're going to kill it.

37:14.080 --> 37:16.360
The Dragon Deity
represents divine justice,

37:16.440 --> 37:18.040
truth and goodness in this world.

37:18.120 --> 37:19.240
Why kill the dragon?

37:19.880 --> 37:23.600
A single thought
can twist a deity into a demon.

37:23.680 --> 37:27.320
Chi Wen once cared for all beings.

37:27.920 --> 37:31.320
But now corrupted by Jiu Ying's taint,

37:31.920 --> 37:33.800
he feeds on them.

37:37.080 --> 37:37.920
Spare me!

37:38.000 --> 37:40.400
I… I don't know anything!

37:41.400 --> 37:42.560
Please!

37:42.640 --> 37:44.000
Let us go!

37:44.080 --> 37:47.040
I need to see my grandson!

37:47.680 --> 37:49.600
It hurts!

37:49.680 --> 37:52.520
Mother, save me!

37:55.360 --> 37:58.960
Peace in this world
often comes at the cost of sacrifice.

37:59.560 --> 38:04.200
Chi Wen's fall
perhaps is for a new balance.

38:05.280 --> 38:07.480
You two must aid the dragon slayer,

38:07.560 --> 38:10.600
gather his power,
and restore order to the world.

38:10.680 --> 38:14.840
Right now, the most urgent thing
is to find the remaining high-rank demons

38:14.920 --> 38:17.080
and take back from them your power.

38:17.800 --> 38:19.000
I know.

38:19.840 --> 38:21.560
We've waited so long.

38:22.440 --> 38:24.400
Finally, this chance has come,

38:25.320 --> 38:28.320
a chance to rightfully take back
my own power.

38:29.840 --> 38:31.080
This mission

38:32.880 --> 38:34.640
must not fail.

38:40.480 --> 38:44.480
Once I gather all four demons' power,
I can slay the dragon myself.

38:44.560 --> 38:45.960
Why rely on someone else?

38:46.840 --> 38:50.160
The Dragon Deity's Power
can only be held by the ancient stone,

38:50.240 --> 38:51.800
the Spirit-Storing Jade.

38:52.640 --> 38:56.720
The jade was split in two by heavenly fire
and forged into magical tools.

38:57.400 --> 39:01.600
One piece is the Spirit-Storing Butterfly
held by the six-eyed butterfly demon.

39:01.680 --> 39:06.800
The other piece is the Spirit-Binding Ring
worn on the Dragon Deity's hand.

39:10.520 --> 39:13.320
Let me wipe your hands. They're all dirty.

39:17.040 --> 39:21.400
So… we just need to take the ring.

39:23.640 --> 39:28.400
After all these centuries,
you're still like a child, so willful.

39:29.600 --> 39:32.840
If you want to try, go ahead.

40:00.880 --> 40:02.160
You Chi!

40:20.920 --> 40:21.760
Ji Ling!

40:23.840 --> 40:25.080
Hide!

40:36.840 --> 40:38.560
This is… wood!

40:39.960 --> 40:40.960
But how can wood bleed?

40:46.120 --> 40:49.120
I don't get it. What's going on?

40:50.920 --> 40:52.800
So you're a puppet.

40:58.400 --> 40:59.520
You're not the Dragon Deity at all!

41:13.800 --> 41:14.760
Li…

41:16.880 --> 41:17.720
Li Jie…
